{"tid":1968434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"127位 歐洲政要聯署反擊譚德塞 讚揚台灣防疫 台外交部：誠摯感謝","createTime":"2020-04-11T16:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T16:55:40.000Z","uid":125168,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9f9c4939c675cd9c3792aee4427aa370c7000f6f","tid":1968434,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T16:02:10.000Z","msg":"世衛總幹事譚德塞連續多日批評台灣，包括斥台灣對他作人身攻擊、否認台灣曾警告武漢肺炎人傳人等。台灣外交部發新聞稿，指歐洲議會 67 位跨黨團議員於 4 月 8 日聯名致函歐盟外交暨安全政策高級代表 Josep Borrell，加上德國國會 60 位跨黨派議員於 4 月 2 日聯署致函世衛總幹事譚德塞，總共 127 位歐洲政要共同發聲，一致讚揚台灣因應新冠病毒的防疫模式值得學習。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/67-%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-60-%E5%BE%B7%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E5%8F%8D%E6%93%8A%E8%AD%9A%E5%BE%B7%E5%A1%9E-%E8%AE%9A%E6%8F%9A%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB-%E5%8F%B0%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8-%E8%AA%A0%E6%91%AF%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F67-%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1-60-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2593%258A%25E8%25AD%259A%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%25A1%259E-%25E8%25AE%259A%25E6%258F%259A%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8-%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E6%2591%25AF%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%25AC%259D%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1Wz2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=af0da898\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F67-%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1-60-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2593%258A%25E8%25AD%259A%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%25A1%259E-%25E8%25AE%259A%25E6%258F%259A%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E5%258F%2